{"tid":2354046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[本土歌影視業與心態] 不要問香港有冇好音樂，要問你有冇支持過做好音樂的人","createTime":"2021-01-05T07:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T10:07:41.000Z","uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8e147d5c515aa73b75782c19893439613d4b49c3","tid":2354046,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:48:54.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108970510452155/posts/426619845353885/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108970510452155%2Fposts%2F426619845353885%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGz1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=a0564e30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108970510452155/posts/426619845353885/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n不要問香港有冇好音樂，要問你有冇支持過做好音樂的人。<br />\n<br />\n叱吒之後，舖天蓋地也是姜濤不值得獎，爭拗林家謙《一人之境》點解冇獎，挪揄關智斌唱了17年的唱功&hellip;&hellip; 過百盞的spotlights，卻沒一盞射向這一對情侶組合，可以說是被嚴重underrated的香港樂團。<br />\n<br />\n他們叫per se (拉丁文，本質)。<br />\n<br />\n家明中學時迷戀《求婚大作戰》，幾乎每集山下智久跑去追長澤美時都會播插曲《小小戀歌》，因而迷上來自沖繩傳奇樂團MONGOL800，青春到不得了，好有希望，好夏天。第一次接觸per se，卻有同樣的感覺，他們愛唱廣東話歌，聽完後會在想「呢隊band竟然係來自香港!?」然後心中暗喜。<br />\n<br />\n第一次聽到per se主音的男聲，有點像日本「凛として時雨」，很陰柔，很非主流；紓情時的歌，又很日本天團「ONE OK ROCK」，再度暗喜一次，「唔洗聽外國band，原來香港都有&hellip;」感到好滿足，一時充滿生機。<br />\n<br />\n叱吒的第十首推介，就是per se《粉碎糖果屋》，你聽完又看過MV之後，你會愛上這個有良心的組合，信我。下了苦功的琴音，加上極吸引的電音，是神來之筆，卻與廣東話這麼匹配。<br />\n<br />\n經常有個比喻，美斯生於香港也可能踢不成波，填鴨教育下做了外賣步兵，但你要問自己，當美斯在追夢踢傑志的時候，你有冇買飛入場睇波？令他不用當外賣員。<br />\n<br />\n當本土的好音樂出現了，你有否珍惜，珍惜仍在唱廣東話，特別是有良知的樂團。<br />\n<br />\n「很想 珍惜的好風光<br />\n你我再看一看 迷路人這願望<br />\n哀傷 打不死的新天國 <br />\n靠你我開創 更艱苦試煉你我」<br />\n- 《粉碎糖果屋》<br />\n<br />\n暗黑怕白晝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FjS50ATT1v0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFjS50ATT1v0&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGz1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=2a3ac84b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FjS50ATT1v0</a> <br />\n(評歌交返畀專業的樂評人，但接受唔到好歌只得21萬點擊！)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cgh1GbQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgh1GbQ.jpg&h=4b23727d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57626de06b498dc8ccdcbc5641210f0d5ee41149","tid":2354046,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d29ff113aba734a2f6d5a6b4078196a9d2785de","tid":2354046,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"08fc72fe0c2c8a665bf610b30cb44bdd9386a641","tid":2354046,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:52:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"70ffa07f35647ed5926ced1b8cef05b14ec834f8","tid":2354046,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6eaa58c1d0ed7ad96d0b25c74cb631816b4936ce","tid":2354046,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:56:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"32eced09b6c78797d5626260b4af6a5f13ec8c0b","tid":2354046,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d7341f13700ae60b5d1e5423e651b8c47e85f2e3","tid":2354046,"uid":162535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c10c3acbd9341deaa5e69082c7ad95d2f5fdc2e6","tid":2354046,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}